data.description: Peaceful, convenient, and affordable townhome centrally located in the heart of Mount Pleasant's coveted Marsh Pointe community.  Upon entering its street, you can see this immaculately kept townhome stands out from the rest with its pristine landscape and eye-catching rose garden - and you haven't even seen the real draw yet! This immaculately kept 1,466 square foot 3BR/3BA end unit nestles up against protected Shem Creek wetlands and accentuates the mossy grand oaks and picturesque marsh-scape you crave from the Lowcountry. Enjoy the outdoor views from the newly constructed private deck with trellis or indoors from the new multi-slide glass doors off your living room. Inside, find a comfortable living space with wood-burning fireplace, and gorgeous low maintenance high end laminateflooring. The kitchen features your most prized upgrades including stainless appliances and a new stove, abundant cabinetry, subway tile backsplash, granite countertops and tile flooring. The first-floor guest room features a custom shiplap vaulted ceiling and a full bath. Upstairs find the master suite with shiplap accent wall, custom built wood barn doors, tiled standing shower and granite vanity. The third bedroom also features the same stylish barn door and the home's third full bathroom.  This townhome not only looks immaculate, but its bones are healthy, too! A new roof was just installed, the chimney was recently cleaned and inspected, and new insulation blown below the raised floor and above in the attic. A new driveway was just added along with a new garage door for the one-car garage. Come and see. Your new home is waiting!
